snippet.title: Duskers - PC 15 Minutes of Gameplay [4k 60FPS] (No Commentary)
snippet.description:
A completely different sort of drone piloting.

Part of my "Braving the Backlog" series where I aim to try out every digital game I own. 
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=1fy8ZKpYEEU&list=PLOFaOI1gkt-AUJ8JSm6mP6Zw5WB0JqGwZ

Duskers was developed and published by Misfits Attic in 2016.
